isbn     ="ISSN~0940-1121",
abstract ="{The talk explains the connection between the Unified Modeling Language
UML and its Object Constraint Language OCL. It shows OCL features by
considering the BART case study and giving a small abstract
specification for it. This specification is animated by means of the
UML Specification Environment USE developed at University of
