original UML and OCL model. We sketch the underlying language features
and indicate how to give a formal interpretation for them.}"
}

@INCOLLECTION{Gogolla:2004:KLUWER,
AUTHOR   ="Martin Gogolla and Paul Ziemann",
TITLE    ="{Checking BART Test Scenarios with UML's Object Constraint Language}",
