automated creation of data exchange specifications from these
platform-specific models is realised by an MDA tool developed in DOL:
The XGenerator allows the validation of UML models against applied
profiles by checking OCL~constraints, and the XGenerator supports a
flexible, MDA based generation of XML~Schema definitions, DocBook
based documentation, and WSDL descriptions.  This paper reports on how
